title: “Stilt” means a space within framework of columns, beams and slabs without enclosure of walls over which the building rests
clause_text: “Stilt” means a space within framework of columns, beams and slabs without enclosure of walls over which the building rests. It is used for parking purposes/other services as provided under these Regulations.
